alternate spp. kukonzera zvirwere zvakasiyana mumbesa dzembatatisi nematomatisi. Blight yekutanga inokonzerwa ne Alternaria solani uye nzvimbo yebrown inokonzerwa ne alternaria alternata zvinowanzoitika, asi chirwere chakaoma chakasiyana zvakanyanya.
alternate marudzi anotora mararamiro akasiyana-siyana. Ivo vanonyanya kurarama sesaprophytes muvhu uye inoora chirimwa zvinhu. Pane alternate mhando, kunyanya A. alternata, izvo zvinokonzeresa allergies muvanhu kana kuti pathogenic muvarwere vasina 
... (3777 chars skipped) ... 
imwe conidia iyo systemically colonize mugadziri kuti aite chechipiri hutachiona pamashizha, madzinde, michero, uye machubhu. Utachiona hunoonekwa zvakanyanya muvanhu vakuru, vanonzwa matishu. Maronda ekutanga kazhinji asingaoneki, uye yechipiri sporulation kunotungamirira kuhutachiona hunorema gare gare mumwaka. Nekuda kwehupamhi hwekugamuchira huwandu hweEBDC, kunyanya A. alternata, inoculum inogona kubva kana kupararira kune yechipiri mauto. Conidiospores ine gobvu, kazhinji melanized, maseru
... (3777 chars skipped) ...
oconazole, harina kunyanya kupararira pane kupikisa kurwisa kufema inhibitors. Zvisinei, DMI-resistant A. alternata zvakaparadzana zvakawanikwa pazvirimwa zvakawanda .

Mukuru anoona nezvehutano mukanzuru yeHarare Dr Prosper Chonzi varamba mashoko ekuti munyika mune chizvarwa chekuChina chakafa nechirwere checoronavirus.
Dr Chonzi vati ongororo yavakaita yakaratidza kuti chainge chisina chirwere ichi.
Chizvarwa chekuChina chechidzimai ichi chakatanga kurwara chiri kwaMutare chichibva chaenda kuna chiremba wacho wekuChina uyo akati chiende kuWest End Clinic.
Asi vanachiremba pachipatara apa vakabva varamba kumuona vachibva vati aendeswe kuWilkins Hospital uko akafa ari munzira.
Dr Chonzi vanoti kune chimwe chizvarwa chekuItaly chakaendeswa kuchipatara ichi chichiti chairwara asi chakazonzi hachinawo chirwere ichi.
Vanhu vanodarika zviuru zvitatu vafa nechirwere checoronavirus pasi rose uye muAfrica chiri kuSouth Africa, Nigeria, Algeria neEgypt. Vabatwa nechirwere ichi pasi rose vanodarika chiuru zana.

Mangwanani Yogis! Nhasi ndi Earth Day uyemanheru ano ndiyo peak of the Lyrids Meteor Shower! Iyi meteor shower ivhareji (20/hr) uye inogadzira nzira dzinopenya, saka edza kubata nyeredzi inopfura kana uine matenga akajeka svondo rino! Saka, tisati tatanga imwe kukurumidza Asana series, ngatimbozororai tichipemberera Earth Day uye tarisa pakunakidzwa nenyika Santosha kudzidzira, kana kubatsira kuchengetedza uye kuedza kwezvakatipoteredza ne ahimsa or Asteya dzidzira nhasi.

Kuyera Nheyo
Online COD sensorinobva pakutorwa kwechiedza che ultraviolet ne organic matter, uye inoshandisa iyo 254 nm spectral absorption coefficient SAC254 kuratidza zviyero zvakakosha zvekuyera zvezvinonyunguduka organic zvinhu zviri mumvura, uye zvinogona kushandurwa kuita COD kukosha mune mamwe mamiriro.Iyi nzira inobvumira kuenderera mberi kwekutarisa pasina kudiwa kwechero reagents.
Main Features
1) Yakananga kunyudza kuyerwa pasina sampling uye pre-kugadzirisa
2) Hapana chemakemikari reagents, hapana kusvibiswa kwechipiri
3) Kurumidza kupindura nguva uye kuenderera kuyerwa
4) Ne otomatiki yekuchenesa basa uye mashoma-kuchengetedza
Application
1) Kuenderera mberi kwekutarisa kweiyo organic zvinhu mutoro mukugadzirisa tsvina
2) Pamhepo-chaiyo-nguva yekutarisisa yekupesvedzera uye kubuda kwemvura yekuchenesa mvura
3) Kushandisa: mvura yepamusoro, mvura inobudisa maindasitiri, uye mvura inobudisa hove nezvimwe

Zvakanaka, iyi sisitimu yekushandisa ikozvino inogona kumhanyisa paPi 2 uye nekuburitswa kwechipiri kunovandudza maficha ekutanga maererano nebhutsu kumhanya uye zvimwe zvakawedzerwa maficha sekugona kupinda neakaundi account yako.
Tsigiro yezvimwe zvikumbiro zvinoshanda izvozvi zvakagadziridzwa zvakare, uye panguva yeChromium OS pachave nekukanganisa kushoma, saka yakagadzikana kuvaka kupfuura yapfuura. Muna 1831 Michael Faraday akawana Electromagnetic induction heat. The basic nheyo yekudzidzira kupisa inzira yakashandiswa yekuwanikwa kwaFaraday. Icho chokwadi ndechekuti, AC ikozvino inoyerera kuburikidza nedunhu inokanganisa mafambiro emagetsi echipiri chedunhu riri pedyo nayo. Kuchinja-chinja kwezvino mukati medunhu rekutanga kwakapa mhinduro yekuti zvisinganzwisisike zvazvino zvinogadzirwa sei munharaunda yechipiri yakavakidzana. Kuwanikwa kwaFaraday kwakakonzera kugadzirwa kwemagetsi emagetsi, majenereta, matransformer, uye michina yekutaurirana isina waya.Kushandiswa kwayo, zvisinei, kwave kusina kukanganisa. Kurasikirwa nekupisa, kunoitika panguva yekupisa yekupisa, kwaive kushamisa kwemusoro kunokanganisa kushanda kwese kwehurongwa. Vatsvaguri vakatsvaga kudzikisira kurasikirwa nekupisa nekumisa magineti mafuremu akaiswa mukati memota kana transformer.
Kurasikirwa nekupisa, kunoitika mukugadzirwa kweelectromagnetic induction, kunogona kushandurwa kuita simba rekupisa rinogadzira mugadziriro yemagetsi nekushandisa mutemo uyu. Maindasitiri mazhinji akabatsirikana kubva mukubudirira kutsva uku nekushandisa induction heat.

Mukuru wesangano reZimbabwe National Council for the Welfare of Children VaMaxim Murungweni vanoti panoda kuita mushandirapamwe munyika dzekuchamhembe kweAfrica kuti dambudziko iri ripere.

Google yakazivisa kuCES kuti Android inowana chinhu chitsva. Zvidzoreso zveMedia zvakaitwa kuti zvive nyore kushandisa. Mimhanzi maapplication anotokutendera iwe kuti uchinje midhiya inoridza pane ipi mudziyo. Heino kuyedza kutsva kwakaitwa neGoogle kugadzira smart madivayiri kushanda zvakanyanya zvisina musono.
Google inoshanda neSpotify pamwe chete kuita kuti ikwanise kushandura midhiya pakati pechero Spotify Connect zvishandiso (vatauri). Google yakazivisawo kuti vari kushanda pane chimwe chinhu chinoona kuti ndeupi mutauriri usina waya wauri pedyo.
Somuenzaniso, paunenge uchifamba-famba, unoenda kune imwe kamuri, uye une mutauriri usina wireless muimba iyoyo zvakare. Foni yako inozongoona kuti ndeupi mutauri ari padhuze uye wokutumira chiziviso ichikumbira midhiya inofanira kuridzwa pane imwe mutauri kana kwete.
Iwe uchagamuchira chiziviso paunosvika kumba mushure mekusiya mota izvo zvinokutendera kuti urambe uchiteerera midhiya yawanga uchitoteerera mumotokari. Foni yako inozoona otomatiki iri padhuze isina waya mutauri chero kwaunenge uri. Maererano neGoogle, foni yako ichashandisa Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, Ultra-wideband (UWB) kuona vatauri vari pedyo.
Hatisati taziva kuti chikamu ichi chichasvika riini. Google inowanzopa maficha paPixel mafoni. Ticharamba tichipanana zvirikuitika mune ramangwana. Unofungei nezveGoogle? Ndokumbira utaure pazasi!

National Railways of Zimbabwe kutanga nemusi weMuvhuro yakaparura chirongwa chekutakura vanhu muguta reBulawayo nezvitima kubva kumusha wevazhinji weCowdray Park kuenda muguta.
Vanhu vakawanda muguta iri vakataura neStudio 7 vati kunyangwe chitima chichinonoka kufamba zviri nani pane vemichovha avo vari kuvabhadharisa mari yakawanda.
Mutauriri weNRZ VaNyasha Maravanyika vanoti change chiri chido chavo kuti zvitima zvakawanda zvibatsire vanhu asi havana mari yekugadzirisa zvimwe zvisiri kushanda zvakanaka sezvo kambani yavo iri kutatarika parizvino.
Muna 2014 NRZ yakambomisa chirongwa chakadai ichiti hachina mari yachaiunza kukambani iyi.

Mufananidzo waLeonardo da Vinci chiratidzo chekuenzanisa, kuongorora uye kubatana pakati pemunhu nedenga. Ingave mune yechokwadi kana abstract maitiro, iyo Vitruvian man tattoo yakasarudzika uye ine chirevo dhizaini iyo pasina mubvunzo ichakonzera kunzwa.

EGL EQUIPMENT SERVICES CO., LTD.(EGL) inyanzvi geophone mutengesi uyo ari muChina, aine chinangwa chekubatanidza zviwanikwa zvakapatsanurwa uye kupa vatengi vedu zvese zvakatenderedza Geophone / Geophysical Zvigadzirwa nemasevhisi ane hukama.
Vese vanovamba veEGL vane zviitiko zveanopfuura makore makumi maviri 'mumunda weGeophone kugadzirwa / Geophysical masevhisi ane dzidzo kumashure kwePHD, Master kana Geophysics Undergraduate Degree.
Iine manejimendi anobudirira, mashandiro akajeka uye mabatiro ane hunhu, EGL yakakwezva mamwe matarenda, nekudaro ichigadzira yakakura uye yakagadzikana timu yehunyanzvi muindasitiri yepamba.
Kwemakore, isu takachengeta hukama hwenguva refu uye hwepedyo hwekubatana nemakoreji akasiyana e geological uye masangano ekutsvagisa muChina, uye nekukasira kusimudzira kwemukati memukati geophysical zviridzwa.Mune vezera rinonakidzwa nemukurumbira wepamusoro, huwandu hwezvigadzirwa mumusha unotungamira nhanho.Isu tinoomerera kumusimboti we "mhando yekutanga, mutengi kutanga", mweya webhizinesi re "vanhu-vanotungamirwa", uye mweya wekuenderera mberi nekupayona uye kuita bhizinesi, nemoyo wese wemudzimba nekune dzimwe nyika kuongorora zvicherwa, Marine exploration, petroleum exploration, geological survey. , matongo, dzidzo uye mamwe maindasitiri evashandisi vazhinji kupa yakanaka geophysical yekuongorora michina!Panguva imwecheteyo kuti kambani igadzire mikana yakawanda uye ramangwana riri nani!

Kutanga, isa yako faira kune yedu PDF compressor.
Chishandiso chedu chinoshandisa yedu compressor otomatiki kutanga kudzikisa uye kumanikidza iyo faira rePDF.
Dhawunirodha iyo yakamanikidzwa PDF faira kune yako komputa
PDF (Portable Document Format), chimiro chakagadzirwa neAdobe, chinova nechokwadi chekutariswa kwepasirese nemavara, mifananidzo, uye fomati. Kubata kwayo, kuchengetedza maficha, uye kutendeseka kwekudhinda kunoita kuti ive yakakosha mumabasa ezvinyorwa, kunze kwekuzivikanwa kwemugadziri wayo.
Compress PDF inosanganisira kudzikisa saizi yefaira regwaro rePDF pasina kukanganisa zvakanyanya kunaka kwayo. Maitiro aya anobatsira pakugadzirisa nzvimbo yekuchengetera, kufambisa kukurumidza kufambisa magwaro, nekuvandudza kugona kwese. Kudzvanya maPDF kunonyanya kubatsira pakugovera mafaera pamhepo kana neemail uchichengeta hunhu hunogamuchirika.

Tungsten Carbide Accelerator
Tsananguro Pfupi:
* Tungsten Carbide, Nickel / Cobalt bhainda
* Sinter-HIP Mavira
* CNC machine
* Sintered, apedza mureza
* Kuwedzera saizi, kushivirira, mamaki uye huwandu zviripo zviripo pakukumbira.
Tungsten carbide accelerators anoshandiswa zvakanyanya pamakemikari michina. Basa hombe nderekuti: Kunaka kwekukuya kunenge kuri nani mukugaya.
Tungsten carbide inogona kumanikidzwa uye kuumbwa kuita akaumbika maumbirwo, inogona kukuyiwa nemazvo, uye inogona kusunganidzwa kana kubatanidzwa kune zvimwe simbi. Mhando dzakasiyana uye mamakisi e carbide anogona kugadzirwa sezvaidikanwa kuti ishandiswe mukushandisa kwakatemerwa, kusanganisira indasitiri yemakemikari, oiri & gasi uye zvegungwa semigodhi nekucheka maturusi, chakuvhe uye kufa, kupfeka zvikamu, nezvimwewo Tungsten carbide inoshandiswa zvakanyanya muindasitiri michina, pfeka zvishandiso zvinodzivirira uye anti-ngura.

Chii chinonzi Profit Revolution Trading Software?
Profit Revolution ishanduko yekutengesa chishandiso munzvimbo ye cryptocurrency. Inopihwa simba nekucheka-kumucheto uye akasimba algorithms, hungwaru hwekugadzira, uye nharembozha mashandiro, iyi intuitive software inopa ongororo yakadzama yemafambisirwo ecryptocurrency uye mafambiro. Ne Profit Revolution, zvinokwanisika kuwana tsvakiridzo yakadzama uye ongororo yemidziyo yedhijitari panguva chaiyo-nguva. Kuwana kurudzi urwu rwe data rakakosha kunoita Profit Revolution imwe yeakanyanya mukurumbira kutengesa software pakati pevatengesi ve crypto pasi rese. Vagadziri vedu vakafungidzira chishandiso chinopa simba wese mushandisi chero padanho rekutengesa uye kuunza vatengesi vatsva vepasi rose munzvimbo yedhijitari yemari uye zviri pachena kuti takabudirira.
Iyo Profit Revolution app ine maturusi ekushandisa ayo akakosha kune vatengesi vecrypto. Iyo app inoshandisa tekinoroji yayo yepamusoro, kugadzira masaini ekupedzisira ekutengesa, kubatsira vatengesi vecrypto kuita sarudzo dzine ruzivo. Yepamberi algorithms simba iyo app kuti iongorore otomatiki misika ye crypto uye uwane kutengeserana kunobatsira kune ese marudzi evatengesi. Kunyangwe iwe uchida kuchengetedza mari yako yawakawana zvakaomarara kana kukura zvakatowedzera, iyo Profit Revolution yakanakira chero mhando yemutengesi.

Pamitambo iyi, maChevrons akakunda Ireland 2-1 mumitambo yeTwenty20, kuchiti weODI wakazopera uri mangange 1-1 sezvo mutambo wekupedzisira usina kuzopera kutambwa nekuti wakakanganiswa nekunaya kwemvura.

Magweta anorwira kodzero dzevanhu, eZimbabwe Lawyers for Human Rights, neChipiri akakwanisa kuburitsa muhusungwa vagari makumi matanhatu nevatanhatu vekuMutirikwi mudunhu reMasvingo vakasungwa neMuvhuro vachipomerwa mhosva yekutyora mutemo une chekuita nemvura, weWater Act.
Hurumende yakamirirwa naVaTrust Mvurume vekuZimbabwe National Water Authority, ZINWA, iri kupomera vagari ava mhosva yekuzvigadza muminda iri kumahombekombe kwedhamu reMutirikwi zvisiri pamutemo kubva muna 2000.
Asi vagari ava, avo vanosanganisira vamwe vane makore anodarika makumi manomwe, vanoti madzisekuru avo aigarawo munzvimbo yavagere iyi uye ndimo mune makuva avo.
Mutongi wedare ramejasitiriti muMasvingo akazopa vagari ava mukana wekutongwa vachibva kudzimba dzavo mushure mekuvabhadharisa mari yechibatiso inoita zana rezviuru zvemadhora emunyika pamunhu, pamusoero pekugara panzvimbo dzavakanyoresa kumapurisa kusvika nyaya iyi yapera.
Gweta riri kumirira vasungwa ava, vari nhengo yesangano remagweta anorwira kodzero dzevanhu, reZimbabwe Lawyers for Human Rights, VaFrank Chirairo, vanoti vasungwa ava vakanzi vadzoke zvakare kudare Muvhuro unouya apo panotarisirwa kutanga kutongwa kwenyaya iyi.
VaChirairo vanoti zvinorwadza kusungwa kwakaitwa vagari ava, uye havana ruzivo rwekuti chii chichaitika kwavari kana vakawanikwa vaine mhosva, kana kuti vakanzi vabve munzvimbo dzavagere havana ruzivo rwekuti vachanzi vanonogara kupi?

Aeon Laser's CEO akagamuchira kubvunzurudzwa kwenhau paSIGN CHINA 2019
Pa19th,Sep, 2019, panzvimbo yedu yeChiratidzo China, Mr Wen CEO weAEON Laser vakabvuma kubvunzurudzwa kwenhau.Kubvunzurudza kwakanangana nezvichangobva kuitika muindasitiri ye laser micromachining uye kusimudzira kwekambani yedu.
Iyi bvunzurudzo zvakare yakavakirwa pamusoro wenyaya- kungwara, kunoenderana nehuzivi hwebhizinesi rekambani yedu, kugadzira zvigadzirwa zvemhando yepamusoro zvevatengi, kupa basa rehunyanzvi uye rine hanya.
Tichachengetawo rudzi urwu rweumhizha uye rega nyika ione simba uye kukwezva kwe "Made in China".
Nguva yekutumira: Sep-20-2019

Kubva munaKurume 15 kusvika 19, 2019, Hebei Depond akagamuchira kugamuchirwa uye kubvumidzwa kweBazi rezvekurima reSudan. Chikwata chekuongorora chakapfuura mazuva mana pamazuva ekuongorora uye kuongorora kwegwaro, uye vakatenda kuti Hebei Depond akasangana ne WHO-GMP manejimendi anodikanwa e Minisitiri yezvekurima yeSudan, ndokupa yakanyanya kuongororwa. Basa rekugamuchira rakapera nekubudirira!
Kuongorora kwakabudirira kwechirimwa ichi neSudan Ministry yezvekurima kunoratidza kuti zvigadzirwa zvekugadzira, hurongwa hwekutarisira mhando uye nharaunda yeHebei Depond zvinoenderana nemaitiro epasi rose e-WHO-GMP, uye zvakazivikanwa zviri pamutemo nehurumende yeSudan, kuisa Nheyo yebhizinesi rekutengesa kunze kwenyika, kusangana nezvinangwa zvebudiriro zekambani, uye nekupa vimbiso yemhando yekutengesa zvigadzirwa mumusika wepamusha, Uye kuwedzera hushamwari hwechinhu chechigadzirwa.
Nguva yekutumira: Chivabvu-08-2020

Runhare
Runhare muchina unoshandiswa kuti vanhu vataure vose vari kure nekure; muchina uyu unofambisa mashoko semagetsi kubudikidza newaya. Runhare rwokutanga rwakagadzirwa nemurume ainzi Graham Bell kunyika yeUnited States of America mumakore emwaka wechikumi 1870.
Pari nhasi runhare rwava muchina wakakoshesa pakufambiswa kwemashoko pakati pedzimba, makambani, mabhizimisi naimo muhushangazhi. Kwave nemhando yerunhare isangashandisi waya asi inoshandisa masaisai inonzi chizinganhare kana kuti cell phone kuEnglish.
Makambani anoita zverunhare muZimbabwe anosanganisira: Africom, Telone, Econet, Telecel neNetone.*
Mamwe Mazwi[chinja | edit source]
Ko iro izwi rokuti runhare rakambovepi?
- -nhara (turn up at some distant place). Chamapiwa akanhara kuJapan - Chamapiwa turned up in Japan.
- Nyakunhara, nhare kana nhara (something that turns up from a distance)?
- Runhare (thin wire).
Mazwi eBantu[chinja | edit source]
- VaYao vanoti kutalikanyana (to be distant from each other) vachireva kuti kutarangana.
- VaYao vanoti kutalika (to be distant) vachireva kuti kure.
- VaYao vanoti chilambo cha kwakutalika (a distant country) vachireva nyika iri kure.
- VaNyakyusa vanoti pa-tali (far) vachireva kuti kure.
- VaNyakyusa vanoti pabu-tali (long) vachireva kuti kurefu kana parefu.

FEP(Fluorinated ethylene propylene),Iyo copolymer ye tetrafluoroethylene uye hexafluoropropylene.FEP inogona kuiswa kumapurasitiki akapfava, uye simba rayo rekusimba, kupfeka kuramba, kuramba kunokambaira kwakadzikira pane akawanda einjiniya mapurasitiki, uye ine yakaderera dielectric inogara pane yakafara tembiricha uye frequency renji.
Izvo zvinhu hazvibatike,it haveyakanakisa kupfeka kuramba uye yakaderera coefficient yekukweshana.Inogona kugadzirwa kuita granular zvigadzirwa zve extrusion uye kuumbauyeinoshandiswa sehupfu hwemibhedha yemvura uye electrostatic kupedzisa,Alsoanogonayakaitwa ma dispersions ane aqueous .Semi-yakapedzwa zvigadzirwa zvinosanganisira mafirimu, mahwendefa, tsvimbo, maelectrode, akakosha-akaumbwa zvikamu uye fibre imwe chete.Mainlykushandiswa ndiko kugadzira mukati memukati wepombi uye makemikari midziyo, iyo yepamusoro layer ye rollers uye waya dzakasiyana-siyana uye tambo.

Bazi rehurumende rinoona nezvehuatno rinoti iri kuronga kuendesa kunze kwenyika vana mukoti, kuitira kuti vanoshanda vari ikoko. Bazi iri rinoti rinoda kuita izvi nekuti harina mari yekubhadhra vana mukoti vose vanenge vapedza zvidzidzo zvekuva vana mukoti.
Mashoko aya akataurwa negurukota rezvehutano, Va Henry Madzorera, muhurukuro yavakaita nebepanhau re Herald. VaMadzorera vanoti sezvo hurumende isina mari, zviri nani kuti pave nehurongwa hwakadai, kuitira kuti vari kutadza kuwana mabasa munyika, vakwanise kushanda kunze kwenyika.
VaMadzorera vanoti idzi ipfungwa dzavainadzo pari zvino, uye kuti izvi zviitike, zvichatora nguva yakareba sezvo nyaya iyi ichifanirwa kutanga yazeiwa nedare remakurukota, uye kana yatambirwa, yoshandiswa sechirongwa chehurumende.
Sachigaro ve Zimbabwe Doctors for Human Rights, Dr Douglas Gwatidzo, vanoti havawirirani nepfungwa dzehurumende.
